description:
collection of textures that can be described as base textures suitable for building up layers or applying straight to surfaces such as stone, plaster, concrete. They work equally well as additional layers to any other textures to add in more detail or roughen them up. This CD has many bonus features such as the panoramic sky maps.

All image maps have been obtained from original photography. Each image is 100% seamless (painted out by hand) and available in two resolutions with a matching bump map. Here is the CD's full contents :-

110 Seamless colour texture maps in both high res 1200x900 and med res 600x450

110 Seamless matching bump maps in both high res 1200x900 and med res 600x450

32 Sky images in both high res 1200x900 and med res 600x450

8 Panoramic skies at super hi res 4000x1000

16 Dirt maps

16 Texture Masks 


